output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. Has CMF: Yes, the post contains "CMF:11240022" which indicates it's electoral propaganda material.
2. Refers to candidate: Yes, it mentions multiple political figures: - Ludovic Orban (presidential candidate) - Chelmus Gheorghe (parliamentary candidate) - Valerian Vreme - Gelu Nicolae Zgavardici
3. Addresses wide population: Yes, this is a paid advertisement with an estimated reach of 45,000-50,000 impressions, clearly targeting a wide audience in the Bacău area.
4. Electoral objective: The post appears to have mixed objectives: - Promotes parliamentary candidate Chelmus Gheorghe - Mentions Ludovic Orban's governance program - Shows campaign activities in Onești
5. Journalism: No, this is clearly campaign material, not journalistic content.
6. Personal opinion: No, this is an official party communication promoting campaign activities.
Important context: While this post promotes both parliamentary and presidential candidates, it's important to note that while parliamentary campaign is still allowed, presidential campaign has ended.

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This post constitutes electoral propaganda because: - Contains CMF number - Is a paid advertisement with significant reach - Promotes both parliamentary and presidential candidates - Shows campaign activities and distribution of electoral materials - Mentions governance program
conclusion.message-for-police: Marketing on Line and Business Advanced Communication - M.O.B.A.C. și Forța Dreptei - Bacău, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin promovarea unui material de propagandă electorală (ID postare Facebook: 1566318563996555) după încheierea perioadei de campanie pentru alegerile prezidențiale. Postarea promovează candidatul la președinție Ludovic Orban și programul său de guvernare, fiind distribuită după ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024, încălcând astfel prevederile legale privind încheierea campaniei electorale. Materialul are caracter electoral evident, fiind marcat cu cod CMF (11240022), și a fost distribuit ca reclamă plătită pe Facebook cu un impact estimat între 45,000-50,000 de afișări.
